title: EDA: understanding the dataset with 3D plots
description: Let's understand the datasetGiven files train_data.zip and test_data.zip - contains JSON files with multiple tables. The most important is sample_data.json, which contains the primary identifiers used in the competition, as well as links to key image / lidar information.  train_images.zip and test_images.zip - contains .jpeg files corresponding to samples in sample_data.json  train_lidar.zip and test_lidar.zip - contains .bin files corresponding to samples in sample_data.json train_maps.zip and test_maps.zip - contains maps of the entire sample area. train.csv - contains all sample_tokens in the train set, as well as annotations in the required format for all train set objects. sample_submission.csv - contains all sample_tokens in the test set, with empty predictions.
